Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.65,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あたまポフポフしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.55,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの袖をつかみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:32.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ピコピコしたらなでて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:35.03,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ゴロゴロしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:40.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心配してにゃいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:43.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し気になるだけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:47.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ニヨニヨしたらそっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}背中借りるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:58.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつまでも　不器用なままよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:04.86,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こっち向いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:07.42,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好き…って言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:23.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたのことを獨り占めしたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:28.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれないの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:37.72,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}繋いていいからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:44.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手をギュしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:24.65,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頭腦昏昏漲漲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抓住你的袖子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:32.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你緩緩地撫摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:35.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想就這麼悠閒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.59,0:22:40.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:43.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是有點在意罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:47.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微笑著 輕輕地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}靠在了背上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:58.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直都這麼地笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:04.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向這邊看過了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:07.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喜歡 說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:23.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想把你獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:28.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然無法變得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:30.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:37.72,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}牽起來就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.82,0:23:44.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:35.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戀の意味なんかわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:38.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたを見つめてたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an9}素直にならないお年頃？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:44.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わかっているのかいないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:48.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}最大のミステリーだだだだだだだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:53.51,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人きり　過ごす日は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:58.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちょっぴり何か足りなくて　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.11,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}みんながそろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やっぱり楽しい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:07.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今は さあ 遊んじゃえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あっちで手を取って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こっちで大騒ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この後のハーモニー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:18.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}みんなで奏でる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あっちで落ち著いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こっちでひと休み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:28.46,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心はぽかぽかして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:37.58,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君がそばにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:15.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}one two three four
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:35.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我不懂所謂的戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:38.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只想一直注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}無法坦率的年齡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:44.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到底是明白還是不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:48.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這是最大的謎題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:53.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}孤獨度過的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:58.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}總感覺少了點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}真的很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:07.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在 走 去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:12.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那裡牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:14.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在這裡很熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}之後的協奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:18.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}由大家來演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在那裡很安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在這裡稍稍休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:28.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心裡暖烘烘的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:37.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為有你陪伴
